### ============================================
### STEP 1: LOGIN FIRST TO GET TOKEN
### ============================================

### Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:54955/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### ============================================
### STEP 2: CREATE PRODUCTS (USING THE TOKEN)
### ============================================

### Create Product 1 - Laptop
POST http://localhost:54955/api/products
Content-Type: application/json


{
    "name": "Gaming Laptop",
    "description": "16GB RAM, 512GB SSD, RTX 4060",
    "sku": "LAP-001",
    "price": 1299.99,
    "stockQuantity": 50,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "active": true
}

