### ============================================
### STEP 3: GET ALL PRODUCTS TO VERIFY
### ============================================

### Get all products (should show all created products)
GET http://localhost:54955/api/products

### DELETE ALL PRODUCTS (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:54955/api/products/all
